
CHANGING MAGIC NUMBER


MOTIVATION:
Changes in requirements can trigger the
adjustment of test cases to handle new cases. A magic number
usually represents specific cases to be tested. If the case
changes, then the magic number also has to be changed.

MECHANICS:
Change magic numbers inside a test method.

